title: How to Build a DIY Skate Gap - Yer Welcome
description:
Legendary skateboarder Pat Duffy teams up with Yer Welcome foreman Kyle Berard to transform a grimy San Diego ditch into a fun skate gap. 
Also featuring; Dolan Stearns, Shaun Ross, Austin Squire, Marius Syvanen, Scott Decenzo, Mark Appleyard, and Ryan Decenzo.
